Post Apartment Homes, L.P. Key Developments

Post Apartment Homes Mulls Acquisitions
Oct 14 15
Post Properties Inc. (NYSE:PPS), which has filed for a shelf registration and its unit is looking for acquisitions. The company stated in its filing that Post Apartment Homes, L.P. intends to use such net proceeds for general corporate purposes including, without limitation, the acquisition and development of multi-family communities and the repayment of debt.


