    improvements, of real estate assets of Post Apartment Homes and
    its Subsidiaries on such date, before depreciation and
    amortization, determined on a consolidated basis in accordance
    with generally accepted accounting principles.


 


 
      
    Unsecured Debt means Debt of Post
    Apartment Homes or any of its Subsidiaries that is not Secured
    Debt.


      
